      "bgName": "ametown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "叶の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kandad001.wav",
      "text": "……叶？　どうしてここに？",
      "startTime": 17.2103404045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お父さん、今日誕生日でしょ！",
      "startTime": 20.3103401501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kan003.wav",
      "text": "だからプレゼント、持って来たの",
      "startTime": 23.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本当はステージの後に渡したかったんだけど",
      "startTime": 25.6053289731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kan004.wav",
      "text": "仕事忙しくて来られないっていうからさ",
      "startTime": 28.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "叶の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ……ああ、ありがとう",
      "startTime": 32.0504309018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "叶の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kandad002.wav",
      "text": "その、叶からプレゼントをもらえるとは思わなかった",
      "startTime": 35.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なんで？",
      "startTime": 40.0170965512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kan005.wav",
      "text": "家族なんだから、誕生日をお祝いするのは当然じゃん",
      "startTime": 41.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12100.000000000002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "叶の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "家族……あ、ああ、そうだな",
      "startTime": 45.4714052518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "叶の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kandad003.wav",
      "text": "………………すまん、ちょっと待っててくれ",
      "startTime": 51.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8781.743876099994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "叶の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『あー……知り合いの子が、たまたま通りかかったんだ",
      "startTime": 54.3380721728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "叶の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kandad004.wav",
      "text": "なんでもないから、先に家に戻っていなさい』",
      "startTime": 58.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………誰、あの人達",
      "startTime": 62.4047368049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kan006.wav",
      "text": "もしかして、お父さんの今の奥さんと…………娘さん？",
      "startTime": 66.9666643779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kan007.wav",
      "text": "……叶、『知り合いの子』なんだ",
      "startTime": 75.3874173164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お父さんにとっての娘は、さっきのあの子だけで",
      "startTime": 80.6083237648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kan008.wav",
      "text": "だから、叶もお父さんの娘だって伝えてくれないんだ",
      "startTime": 86.8000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "叶の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ、い、いや、そんなつもりじゃなかったんだ",
      "startTime": 93.1128815651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "叶の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kandad005.wav",
      "text": "……叶が、そこまで英語が分かると思わなくて……",
      "startTime": 96.6000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "生まれてすぐお母さんは死んじゃってるから……",
      "startTime": 99.97954518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kan009.wav",
      "text": "叶のお父さんは、叶の家族は、お父さん一人だけだし",
      "startTime": 104.1966041252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "小さい頃、沢山可愛がってくれたことも",
      "startTime": 110.8026292483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kan010.wav",
      "text": "それが、凄く嬉しかったのも覚えてる",
      "startTime": 115.0000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だから、お父さんに会いたいってずっと思ってたし",
      "startTime": 120.0858497302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kan011.wav",
      "text": "連絡くれた時、凄く嬉しかったの",
      "startTime": 125.2666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でもお父さんからしたら、叶は『家族』じゃないのかな",
      "startTime": 129.8889791171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "小島叶",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kan012.wav",
      "text": "お父さんにとって、叶ってなんなの？",
      "startTime": 139.5338716805,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cup-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8210.345206699998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night"
    },
    {
