      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい、温かいコーヒーを淹れたから飲みなさい",
      "startTime": 147.7442168872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-mhk001.wav",
      "text": "……それで、少しは落ち着いた？",
      "startTime": 152.9358620755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うーん……結局、あんたのパパ",
      "startTime": 156.2934009235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kor001.wav",
      "text": "テレビ見た後、なんでわざわざ連絡してきたの？",
      "startTime": 160.8774854978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうよね。今の家族に貴方のことを隠していたなら",
      "startTime": 165.1600675901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-mhk002.wav",
      "text": "見つけた後も、そのまま黙っておけば良かったのに",
      "startTime": 170.2688835542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "小さい頃、「お前の父親は病気だからもう会えない」",
      "startTime": 173.4928567251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_05-kan013.wav",
      "text": "ってある日突然、爺に言われたの",
      "startTime": 178.1052404722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "信じられる訳なくて。クソ爺がお父さんとkanaに",
      "startTime": 181.896280702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
